    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1307">
<l>ūṭali ṉuṇṭāṅkōr tuṉpam puṇarvatu </l>
<l>nīṭuva taṉṟuko loṉṟu.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The doubt as to whether intercourse would take place soon or not, creates a sorrow (even) in feigned dislike.</l>
            </lg>
